com.revolsys.jts.operation.distance3d

Class AxisPlaneCoordinateSequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revolsys.jts.geom.impl.AbstractGeometry
      • com.revolsys.jts.geom.impl.AbstractLineString
        • com.revolsys.jts.operation.distance3d.AxisPlaneCoordinateSequence
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataTypeProxy, Geometry, Lineal, LineString, Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<Object>

    public class AxisPlaneCoordinateSequence
extends AbstractLineString
    A LineString wrapper which projects 3D coordinates into one of the three Cartesian axis planes, using the standard orthonormal projection (i.e. simply selecting the appropriate ordinates into the XY ordinates). The projected data is represented as 2D coordinates.
    Author:
    mdavis
